---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead
			title="About CambrianMusic™"
			description="Cambrian is building the marketplace layer for AI-native music licensing and creator income."
		/>
		<style>
			main {
				width: var(--max-width-wide);
				max-width: calc(100% - 2em);
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 3em 1em 4em;
			}
			.hero {
				max-width: 780px;
				margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
			}
			.eyebrow {
				font-size: 0.75rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.1em;
				color: var(--label-color);
				margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
			}
			.hero h1 {
				margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
			}
			.hero p {
				font-size: 1.05rem;
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				line-height: 1.7;
			}
			.grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
				gap: 1.5rem;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}
			.panel {
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
				border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
				background: var(--bg-card);
			}
			.panel h2 {
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
			}
			.panel p,
			.panel li {
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				line-height: 1.7;
			}
			.panel ul {
				margin: 0;
				padding-left: 1.25rem;
			}
			.cta {
				padding: 1.75rem;
				border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
				border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
				background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 255, 153, 0.05), rgba(0, 255, 153, 0.02));
			}
			.cta p {
				color: var(--text-secondary);
			}
			.actions {
				display: flex;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				gap: 0.75rem;
				margin-top: 1rem;
			}
			.button {
				display: inline-flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
				border-radius: 999px;
				font-weight: 600;
				text-decoration: none;
			}
			.button-primary {
				background: var(--accent);
				color: var(--bg-primary);
			}
			.button-secondary {
				border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
				color: var(--text-primary);
			}
			@media (max-width: 720px) {
				main {
					padding: 2em 1em 3em;
				}
				.grid {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section class="hero">
				<p class="eyebrow">About CambrianMusic™</p>
				<h1>The marketplace layer for AI-native music</h1>
				<p>
					Cambrian exists because AI music is already a real economy, but most of the infrastructure around licensing, discovery, and monetization still assumes an older market. We are building for the creators and buyers operating in that new reality.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="grid">
				<div class="panel">
					<h2>What Cambrian does</h2>
					<p>
						Cambrian gives creators a direct path from track to commerce. Instead of uploading music into a system built for exposure alone, creators can package tracks with clear licensing, set pricing, and sell to buyers who need music for actual commercial use.
					</p>
					<p>
						For buyers, the value is speed and clarity. They can find tracks, understand the rights, and move forward without guessing what is allowed.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="panel">
					<h2>Who it serves</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>AI-native musicians building commercial catalogs</li>
						<li>Content creators and brands sourcing ready-to-use tracks</li>
						<li>Agencies, startups, and developers shipping with sound on a deadline</li>
						<li>Buyers who need music with licensing confidence, not ambiguity</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="grid">
				<div class="panel">
					<h2>Why this blog exists</h2>
					<p>
						The blog focuses on the commercial side of AI music: pricing, licensing, catalog strategy, metadata, buyer behavior, and the platform shifts that determine whether tracks actually sell.
					</p>
					<p>
						The goal is utility. Every post should help creators make better decisions and help buyers understand where the market is going.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="panel">
					<h2>What Cambrian believes</h2>
					<p>
						Creation is no longer the bottleneck. Discovery, licensing clarity, and monetization are. The platforms that win will be the ones built around that reality from the start.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="cta">
				<h2>Build a catalog that can actually sell</h2>
				<p>
					Explore the latest guides or go straight to Cambrian and start publishing tracks into a marketplace designed for commercial use.
				</p>
				<div class="actions">
					<a class="button button-primary" href="https://cambrianmusic.com/login?register=true">Create account</a>
					<a class="button button-secondary" href="/blog/">Read the blog</a>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
